messages.content: What is the purpose of ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix?
ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix is a custom node for SDXL LCM in ComfyUI that accelerates image generation while ensuring consistency before and after acceleration, making it ideal for bulk image production.
To install ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix, simply place the library in the 'ComfyUI/custom_nodes/' directory.
What is the default cache interval for ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix?
The default cache interval for ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix is 3 steps.
What is the default cache depth for ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix?
The default cache depth for ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix is 3.
At what step does ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix start using the cache by default?
ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix starts using the cache at step 0 by default.
At what step does ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix stop using the cache by default?
ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix stops using the cache at step 12 by default.
Is input layer caching enabled by default in ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix?
Yes, input layer caching is enabled by default in ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix.
Is middle layer caching enabled by default in ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix?
Yes, middle layer caching is enabled by default in ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix.
Is output layer caching enabled by default in ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix?
Yes, output layer caching is enabled by default in ComfyUI-DeepCache-Fix.
